org.nasdanika.html.model.bootstrap

Interface TableCell

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Adaptable, BootstrapElement, EObject, HtmlElement, Marked, ModelElement, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TableCellImpl

    public interface TableCell
extends BootstrapElement
    A representation of the model object 'Table Cell'. Table cell - regular or header.

    The following features are supported:

    • Header
    • Col Span
    • Row Span
    • Color
    • Background
    See Also:
    BootstrapPackage.getTableCell()
